# Paste each line as a separate variable in Vercel:
# Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#
# Name                      Value
# ------------------------  --------------------------------------------------
# JWT_SECRET                (copy from .env - 32+ characters)
# SUPABASE_URL              (copy from .env)
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY         (copy from .env)
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY (copy from .env)
# MAX_USERS                 0   (0 = unlimited)
# ADMIN_USERNAME            (copy from .env)
# ADMIN_PASSWORD            (copy from .env)
